  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Metrogether</strong> is a train simulator where you drive, collect passengers, work together with friends and explore the subway network in a fictional city. Embark on your journey as a train driver, dispatcher or ticket inspector in single and multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drive Trains</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of a subway train, try to follow the timetable and collect passengers as you travel from station to station in this immersive subway simulation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/41be5ce862371ca93ff46ea6c21846be.poster.avif?t=1773353712\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/41be5ce862371ca93ff46ea6c21846be.webm?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/41be5ce862371ca93ff46ea6c21846be.mp4?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the Subway Network</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in this fictional subway network, filled with tunnels, bustling stations, and hidden secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/5e0cca86d10f5145f7ec4bbc1d750087.poster.avif?t=1773353712\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/5e0cca86d10f5145f7ec4bbc1d750087.webm?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/5e0cca86d10f5145f7ec4bbc1d750087.mp4?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play as a Dispatcher</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter a dispatcher office, start seting train routes and make sure trains arrive at their destination on time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/d4c4563caa6e0dffafaeb3afcaac21d1.poster.avif?t=1773353712\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/d4c4563caa6e0dffafaeb3afcaac21d1.webm?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/d4c4563caa6e0dffafaeb3afcaac21d1.mp4?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play as a Ticket Inspector</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of a vigilant ticket inspector, ensuring that passengers have valid tickets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/bb7678605c0b53991a0f95986cf2e473.poster.avif?t=1773353712\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/bb7678605c0b53991a0f95986cf2e473.webm?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/bb7678605c0b53991a0f95986cf2e473.mp4?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play together with your Friends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join forces with friends or strangers to explore the subway network together. You can team up with one player driving and another checking tickets, or take on different journeys in the same world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/fff6c457c23292979412b840a555c9bc.poster.avif?t=1773353712\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/fff6c457c23292979412b840a555c9bc.webm?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/fff6c457c23292979412b840a555c9bc.mp4?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Train Simulation:</strong> Drive trains with realistic physics, obey speed limits, stop at stations and signals, collect passengers and check tickets.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open World:</strong> Explore the Open World by train or on foot.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No fail screens:</strong> There are no fail screens, even when you run a stop signal or cause an accident.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online Multiplayer:</strong> Play in Multiplayer with lots of other players simultaneously.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Character Selection:</strong> Choose from a variety of characters. Try roleplaying to fit in or pick something out of the ordinary; the choice is yours.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Metrogether</strong> is a train simulator where you drive, collect passengers, work together with friends and explore the subway network in a fictional city. Embark on your journey as a train driver, dispatcher or ticket inspector in single and multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drive Trains</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of a subway train, try to follow the timetable and collect passengers as you travel from station to station in this immersive subway simulation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/41be5ce862371ca93ff46ea6c21846be.poster.avif?t=1773353712\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/41be5ce862371ca93ff46ea6c21846be.webm?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/41be5ce862371ca93ff46ea6c21846be.mp4?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the Subway Network</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in this fictional subway network, filled with tunnels, bustling stations, and hidden secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/5e0cca86d10f5145f7ec4bbc1d750087.poster.avif?t=1773353712\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/5e0cca86d10f5145f7ec4bbc1d750087.webm?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/5e0cca86d10f5145f7ec4bbc1d750087.mp4?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play as a Dispatcher</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter a dispatcher office, start seting train routes and make sure trains arrive at their destination on time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/d4c4563caa6e0dffafaeb3afcaac21d1.poster.avif?t=1773353712\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/d4c4563caa6e0dffafaeb3afcaac21d1.webm?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/d4c4563caa6e0dffafaeb3afcaac21d1.mp4?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play as a Ticket Inspector</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of a vigilant ticket inspector, ensuring that passengers have valid tickets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/bb7678605c0b53991a0f95986cf2e473.poster.avif?t=1773353712\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/bb7678605c0b53991a0f95986cf2e473.webm?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/bb7678605c0b53991a0f95986cf2e473.mp4?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play together with your Friends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join forces with friends or strangers to explore the subway network together. You can team up with one player driving and another checking tickets, or take on different journeys in the same world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/fff6c457c23292979412b840a555c9bc.poster.avif?t=1773353712\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/fff6c457c23292979412b840a555c9bc.webm?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239770/extras/fff6c457c23292979412b840a555c9bc.mp4?t=1773353712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Train Simulation:</strong> Drive trains with realistic physics, obey speed limits, stop at stations and signals, collect passengers and check tickets.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open World:</strong> Explore the Open World by train or on foot.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No fail screens:</strong> There are no fail screens, even when you run a stop signal or cause an accident.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online Multiplayer:</strong> Play in Multiplayer with lots of other players simultaneously.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Character Selection:</strong> Choose from a variety of characters. Try roleplaying to fit in or pick something out of the ordinary; the choice is yours.</p></li></ul>",
